The `near` positional operator has the following syntax:

```json
{
  "$search": {
    "span": {
      "near": {
        "clauses": [
          { <span-positional-or-term-operator-specification> },
          ...
        ],
        "slop": <distance-number>,
        "inOrder": true|false
      }
    }
  }
}
```
